item.title:
Taylor Swift announces ‘Midnights (The Til Dawn Edition),’ out this Friday.
It features a remix of “Karma” featuring Ice Spice, a new version of “Snow On The Beach” with “more Lana,” and “Hits Different.”
item.author: popcrave

item.title:
Taylor Swift announces “Snow On The Beach (Feat. More Lana Del Rey),” releasing this Friday:
“Lana and I went back into the studio specifically to record more Lana on Snow on the Beach. Love u Lana ”
